  "detailed_description": "<h1>Just Updated</h1><p>With the last update I added an endless mode to the game with an infinite amount of puzzles.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942000/extras/7170089f12013cea19e3047aad2db34f.poster.avif?t=1661890381\" width=612 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942000/extras/7170089f12013cea19e3047aad2db34f.webm?t=1661890381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942000/extras/7170089f12013cea19e3047aad2db34f.mp4?t=1661890381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Combine, rotate and move different shapes to solve puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942000/extras/7a09559d4b3f8a6520e9c47e9971b55c.poster.avif?t=1661890381\" width=612 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942000/extras/7a09559d4b3f8a6520e9c47e9971b55c.webm?t=1661890381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942000/extras/7a09559d4b3f8a6520e9c47e9971b55c.mp4?t=1661890381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are 80 different puzzles available at the time of release. With increasing difficulty for several hours of puzzling fun. Afterwards you can play the <strong>endless mode</strong> with an infinite amount of generated puzzles.<br><br>Get to know all field types and face the most complicated puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942000/extras/5f18f113b5301116b6be94fddb3d1f41.poster.avif?t=1661890381\" width=612 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942000/extras/5f18f113b5301116b6be94fddb3d1f41.webm?t=1661890381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942000/extras/5f18f113b5301116b6be94fddb3d1f41.mp4?t=1661890381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game will get some updates with more content customisation options.",
